Package: geneOptimize
Type: Package
Title: An Object-Oriented Framework for Genetic Algorithms and Variable
        Selection in R
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hui", "Zheng", email = "huizheng1@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Maintainer: Hui Zheng <huizheng1@gmail.com>
Description: An R6-based framework for genetic and memetic algorithms.
  Supports binary and real-valued encodings, modular operators,
  parallel fitness evaluation via 'future', and hybridization with
  local search. Designed for variable selection, hyperparameter
  optimization, and general optimization problems.
License: MIT
